data.description: **Seller is offering a $5,000 contribution to a buyer's closing costs!** Come tour this spacious three bedroom home in the heart of residential Sulphur, just minutes from everything. Nestled on an ample sized lot, the freshly painted brick home boasts an oversized carport, lengthy driveway, fenced rear yard and metal storage building. The numerous floor to ceiling windows provide abundant natural light into the open concept living area and renovated kitchen. An oversized kitchen island overlooking the dining room space provides plenty of room for entertainment. An ample second living area could be used as spacious fourth bedroom. The abundant utility room could provide additional space for an office or craft room. Schedule your showing today!
